class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/clausgib33\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1913cfaa86edc011c8039d9e0ba0e43c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1913cfaa86edc011c8039d9e0ba0e43c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/clausgib33\" class=\"reviewer-name\">clausgib33</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Only 20 images!!!\nDo not use\ndescription deceptive. \n\nPoor poor poor</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent Gallery Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dashard\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7381590cc329d4024b163ea0c7fb268e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7381590cc329d4024b163ea0c7fb268e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dashard\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dashard</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 2, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This has a very nice balance of features/ease of use. The options available are very well thought out, and the galleries look terrific. I especially like the various Lightbox options built in. Saves me from having to graft a preferred lightbox on via functions.\n\nAll in all, excellent performance, value and presentation.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Love it!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/asha2012\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/67d689c7781970a4c2859fffe49969c2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/67d689c7781970a4c2859fffe49969c2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/asha2012\" class=\"reviewer-name\">almh <small>(asha2012)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 2, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It can be a bit tricky to get the mosaic results you want, but after some fudging I typically end up with something I am happy with. Plus the lightbox is great and comes with the free version. Good enough!\n\nHappy to have found this little tool.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Galleries</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stephenkh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f4256c865414cc7a9108c6a7b72a00e0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f4256c865414cc7a9108c6a7b72a00e0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stephenkh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stephenkh</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 1, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The galleries are fairly easy to work with and offer quite a number of features. Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">WOW- Spectacularly Easy to Use! :)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bitofgrace\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6d7f21f01279181dc5d52c3c8da7d6bf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6d7f21f01279181dc5d52c3c8da7d6bf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bitofgrace\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bitofgrace</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Am impressed and satisfied. I was hunting for a paid Elementor plugin to make up for gaps and spacing getting crazy out of control in the WP galleries only to find this free solution that works intuitively like a charm with some of the extra features that so many plugins are charging big $ for.  Thrilled! and happy to donate to its support. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good pruduct, good support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tudala\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0f6c05c8f13e6d99c6c08b72e97b556?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0f6c05c8f13e6d99c6c08b72e97b556?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tudala\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tudala</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 29, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Real useful plugin, better than other gallery plugin as the display effect is great enough without any setting. The technical support is very in-time and they solve my problem immediately.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Much better than others</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anbucco\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d0535386e8eafd83386ebe4a188b3a21?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d0535386e8eafd83386ebe4a188b3a21?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anbucco\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anbucco</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 29, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">After running into trouble with the \"other\" gallery plug-in on many of my sites I switched over to Modula. I’m having no hassles so far and great performance. Since it doesn’t create \"own\" folders I recommend a media organizer plug-in (as always...)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Loving Modula Pro</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mphaynes\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50713770c2d9e209a1e446d638e87b92?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/50713770c2d9e209a1e446d638e87b92?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mphaynes\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mphaynes</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 26, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have a client who has hundreds of individual photo galleries on his websites. Adding Modula to my mix of tools has seriously improved my ability to manage these galleries.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:102:\"Photo Gallery by Modula - an advanced solution for Photo Gallery users. Create beautiful image&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin