n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/isabellabanksphotography\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2c3cdb9faf8c65b0b0628dbc28102e11?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2c3cdb9faf8c65b0b0628dbc28102e11?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/isabellabanksphotography\" class=\"reviewer-name\">isabellabanksphotography</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">So awesome. Thank you</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No ReCaptcha and Not Good with Elementor</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gregoryherring\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08a19b4448157ac1a59a5d75eaa1f3a7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08a19b4448157ac1a59a5d75eaa1f3a7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gregoryherring\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gregory.herring</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I read in some of your other responses that reCAPTCHA was free to use with your plugin.  I set it up, make a simple form and the box to \'drag-n-drop\' reCAPTCHA is listed under \'Fancy Fields\'.  When I try to drag it over I get the message:\n\nCaptcha Field is a Pro Feature\nWe\'re sorry, the Captcha Field is not available on your plan. Please upgrade to the PRO plan to unlock all these awesome features.\n\nThere are quite a few plugin forms out there where reCAPTCHA is a free addition or it is just included in the plugin for free.  \n\nFurthermore, in the fancy fields there are several very common, NOT fancy items that should be indigenous to every contact form these days such as Phone Number, Address and Website URL. Not paying for that...\n\nI\'ve been using Elementor for awhile (2 years straight)  now and when I try and change the color of the text in the contact form - no dice. So I can not get it to blend in well with my theme.\n\nThis plugin is being pushed by a lot of theme developers so you guys must have one heck of an affiliate program but I\'m not buying it.\n\nI\'ll stick with the tried and true Contact Form plugin. It blends well with themes, reCAPTCHA is free and I don\'t have to pay for standard features.\n\nWish you guys the best\n\n </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">WP contact form</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org